headline.print_headline: Australia Consider Response to FIFA Bid Report Criticism
headline.main: Australia Consider Response to FIFA Bid Report Criticism

lead_paragraph: Federation Football Australia (FFA) said it would review the findings of the FIFA report into the 2018 and 2022 World Cup bidding process before addressing the alleged wrongdoing of its bid.
